name: Chrome Dino 🦖 ~ Instant Death
description:
This is the 1st Piece in a series of 3. 

An often-overlooked Easter Egg in Google Chrome is the dinosaur game, which appears when you try to visit a website while disconnected from the Internet. The Chrome Dino game is a play on going back to the 'prehistoric age' when you had no Wi-Fi.

It's a simple infinite runner, which sees you jump over cacti, and dodge underneath obstacles.
